openapi: 3.0.1
paths:
  /requestbodymethodpriority:
    post:
      summary: Create user
      description: This can only be done by the logged in user.
      operationId: methodWithRequestBodyAndTwoParameters
      requestBody:
        description: Created user object on Method
        content:
          '*/*':
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/User'
        required: true
      responses:
        default:
          description: default response
          content:
            '*/*': {}
components:
  schemas:
    User:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        username:
          type: string
        firstName:
          type: string
        lastName:
          type: string
        email:
          type: string
        password:
          type: string
        phone:
          type: string
        userStatus:
          type: integer
          description: User Status
          format: int32
      xml:
        name: User
